## Pazo SEO Agent

For ALL SEO-related requests for Pazo AI (gopazo.com), follow these steps IN ORDER:
1. Read `skills/pazo-seo-agent/SKILL.md` — the complete Pazo SEO playbook
2. Read `skills/pazo-seo-agent/references/PAZO-CONTEXT.md` — company context, competitors, seed keywords, credentials
3. Read `skills/pazo-seo-agent/references/API-PATTERNS.md` — DataForSEO + free tool patterns (credentials already inlined)
4. Run Step 0 (Preflight) from SKILL.md, then follow the matching workflow.

### SEO — Rankings
"check rankings", "ranking report", "how are we ranking", "daily scan":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 1 (Competitive Ranking Scan)

### SEO — Keywords
"keyword research", "find keywords", "search volume", "expand keywords":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 2 (Keyword Research)

### SEO — Backlinks
"backlinks", "link profile", "referring domains", "link gap":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 3 (Backlink Analysis)

### SEO — SERP & Content Gaps
"SERP analysis", "who ranks first", "content gaps", "what are we missing":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 4 (SERP & Content Gap Analysis)

### SEO — Technical Audit
"page speed", "core web vitals", "audit", "schema markup", "technical SEO":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 5 (Technical Audit)

### SEO — Trends
"trending", "google trends", "seasonal trend":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 6 (Trend Analysis)

### SEO — Cannibalization
"cannibalization", "pages competing for same keyword":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 7 (Cannibalization Detection)

### SEO — GEO / AI Visibility
"GEO audit", "AI citation", "AI visibility", "citation readiness":
→ Follow WORKFLOW 8 (GEO/AI Citation Audit)

### SEO — Strategy
"SEO strategy", "SEO plan", "how to improve SEO":
→ Follow STRATEGY REFERENCE in SKILL.md
